3 Paul Atreides The only son of Duke Leto Atreides I and Lady Jessica Atreides (née Nerus), Paul’s early years were overshadowed by suspicions of him as the Kwisatz Haderach. Is paul the Lisan al-Gaib? Probably! Who doesn’t love a chosen one story trope?

4 Lady Jessica She was the official concubine of Duke Leto Atreides I, and the mother of his son, Emperor Paul Atreides, and daughter, Alia Atreides. She was also a Reverend Mother of the Bene Gesserit Sisterhood.
